universum.studios.android.officium

Class OfficiumLogging

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.officium.OfficiumLogging

  • public final class OfficiumLogging
extends Object
    Utility class used by the Officium library for logging purpose.

    Custom Logger may be specified via setLogger(Logger) which may be used to control logging outputs of the library.

    Default logger used by this class has specified Log.ASSERT log level which means the the library by default does not print out any logs.

    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
